ing, or will the sun see you setting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > This game is designed mobile-first, it is available on the Google Play store under the name : Samurai Dungeon Offline Loot. Worry not, the PC version has no ads and IAPs.    <br>Music by Makai Symphony, Icons from </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
